The paper discusses the security and privacy concerns related to machine learning as a service, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The proposed solution involves executing the machine learning model locally on the user's client, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also discusses the applicability of the proposed solution to offline applications, which falls under the category of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
